flowchart TD
    Start([Mulai]) --> Request[Request Prediksi Nutrisi]
    Request --> Validasi{Request Valid?}
    Validasi -->|Tidak| Error[Error: Request Tidak Valid]
    Validasi -->|Ya| AmbilData[Ambil 7 Data Terakhir]
    AmbilData --> ProsesData[Proses Data untuk LSTM]
    ProsesData --> LoadModel[Load Model LSTM]
    LoadModel --> Prediksi[Jalankan Prediksi LSTM]
    Prediksi --> Hasil[Hasil Prediksi Nutrisi]
    Hasil --> Simpan[Simpan ke Database]
    Simpan --> Tampilkan[Tampilkan Hasil Prediksi]
    Tampilkan --> Selesai([Selesai])
    Error --> Selesai

    classDef start fill:#2ecc71,stroke:#27ae60,color:#fff
    classDef process fill:#3498db,stroke:#2980b9,color:#fff
    classDef decision fill:#f39c12,stroke:#e67e22,color:#fff
    classDef ml fill:#e74c3c,stroke:#c0392b,color:#fff
    classDef success fill:#27ae60,stroke:#2ecc71,color:#fff
    classDef error fill:#c0392b,stroke:#a93226,color:#fff

    class Start start
    class Request,AmbilData,ProsesData,LoadModel,Prediksi,Hasil,Simpan,Tampilkan process
    class Validasi decision
    class Error error
    class Selesai success
